constraint: The DNA sequence shall only contain letters A, T, C and G.
The length of The DNA sequence shall be at least 10.
The length of The DNA sequence shall be a multiple of three.
The DNA sequence shall start with ATG.
The DNA sequence shall end with either TAA, or TAG, or TGA.
result: (or (= suffix s "TAA") (= suffix s "TAG") (= suffix s "TGA"))
